    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition car that should make a solid choice for someone looking for a clean, dependable driver without paying mint-condition money. It presents nicely overall, with the kind of light cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from normal use, but nothing that takes away from it as a usable, attractive vehicle. The interior should be tidy and comfortable, and overall it appears to have been cared for rather than neglected. Buyers should expect a car that shows well, drives like a proper good-condition example, and offers a nice balance between value and condition.",
