      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle offered with honest value in mind. This car shows its age but remains an appealing option for buyers seeking inexpensive transportation, a starter vehicle, or a project opportunity. Priced to move and presented as a straightforward purchase with real affordability.",
