      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has the kind of honest, well-used character you\u2019d expect at this price, and for the right buyer it could be a great little opportunity. If you\u2019re practical, handy, or just want something inexpensive to get started with, this one is worth a look.",
